Class ComplianceReport

java.lang.Object
  com.moki.aem.data.model.ComplianceReport
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class ComplianceReport
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Represents a Compliance Report indicating if the device is compliance based on the sum of all checks. A risk score is also provided where a risk of 0 is the ideal state. This class also provides the devices Geo-Location and a list of each compliance check.
